1. var vs let & const

var: available since ... ever, function & global scope
let & const: available since ES6, block scope

Ex:
function getName(){
  if (isValid) {
    var name = "Quan";
    console.log(name)
  }
  console.log(name) -> out of block -> still working
  //Nếu thay thế var thành let hoặc const sẽ báo lỗi
}


